name: MySQL5

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond: ( ( t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 1  OR  t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 2  OR  t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 3  OR  t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 4  OR  t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 5  OR  t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 6  OR  t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 7 ) )
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

queryCode:
SELECT
t1.`CREATE_DATE`,
t1.`CREATE_UID`,
t1.`DAY_NUMBER`,
t1.`ID`,
t1.`NAME`,
t1.`RULE_ID`,
t1.`SHIFT_ID`,
t1.`WRITE_DATE`,
t1.`WRITE_UID`
FROM `ATTENDANCE_WORKDAY` t1
